	* Makefile.in: use environment varables provided by pkg-config.

2008-01-23  Takeshi Abe  <tabe@fixedpoint.jp>

	* release 0.2.0.

2008-01-22  Takeshi Abe  <tabe@fixedpoint.jp>

	* mm_avcodec.c, mm_avcodec.h, mm_avcodec.types, mm_avcodeclib.stub: new.
	They will serve to provide the skelton of libavdevice; for now solely
	avdevice-version.
	* multimedia/avdevice.scm: ditto.

	* test/test.scm: check avdevice-version.
	* Makefile.in: build mm_avdevice; added -lavdevice to libs.
	* mm_ffmpeg.h: include mm_avdevice.h.
	* multimedia/ffmpeg.scm: extend multimedia.avdevice.
	* doc/reference.scm: described avdevice-version.

2007-12-18  Takeshi Abe  <tabe@fixedpoint.jp>

	* multimedia/ffmpeg.scm (call-with-input-avcodec): changed its semantics;
	escape from current continuation does *not* close codec contexts, like
	call-with-input-file's behavior on the port.

